item.title: How do i tele someone to me need code?
item.dc:creator: @kiwon kiwon
item.description:
@kiwon wrote:

[code] if (command.startsWith(“xteletome”) && (playerRights > 0)) {
try {
String otherPName = command.substring(10);
int otherPIndex = PlayerHandler.getPlayerID(otherPName);

				if (otherPIndex != -1) {
					client p = (client) server.playerHandler.players[otherPIndex];

					p.teleportToX = absX;
					p.teleportToY = absY;
					p.heightLevel = heightLevel;
					p.updateRequired = true;
					p.appearanceUpdateRequired = true;
					p.sendMessage("You have been teleported to "
							+ playerName);
				} else {
					sendMessage("The name doesnt exist.");
				}
			} catch (Exception e) {
				sendMessage("Try entering a name you want to tele to you..");
			}
		}[/code]

item.title: How do i tele someone to me need code?
item.dc:creator: @Java_Is_My_Bitch Java Is My Bitch™
item.description:
@Java_Is_My_Bitch wrote:

You don’t need to type an underscore.

It would just be xteletome and a space, and the name following after that.

::xteletome player

player would be the person that would be teled to you.
